<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10626441>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Serpulid Propomatoceros permianus sp. nov. from the Sosio Valley, western Sicily (Italy), Wordian to upper Permian, holotype MSNC 4526. A. General view of the tube encrusting a sponge. B, C. SEM images, general view (B) and detail of the tube (C) showing denticles of the median keel and the equally spaced transverse ribs. D. Detail of the median keel bearing inconspicuous denticles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10626441/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

